ZH: 我有一匹马。
EN: I have a horse.
ZH: 这匹马很快。
EN: This horse is very fast.
ZH: 他们正在赛马场上骑着匹马。
EN: They are riding a horse on the racetrack.
ZH: 我看到一匹漂亮的白马。
EN: I saw a beautiful white horse.
ZH: 在草原上，有一匹褐色的马在吃草。
EN: There is a brown horse grazing in the grassland.
ZH: 王子骑着一匹黑马。
EN: The prince is riding a black horse.
ZH: 每匹马都有自己的名字。
EN: Each horse has its own name.
ZH: 这匹马是我的最爱。
EN: This horse is my favorite.
ZH: 她每天都会梳理她的匹马。
EN: She brushes her horses every day.
ZH: 小男孩向商店看了一匹玩具马。
EN: The little boy looked at a toy horse in the store.
ZH: 骑兵骑着一匹快马往前冲。
EN: The cavalry rode a fast horse forward.
ZH: 骑手正在训练匹马跳过障碍。
EN: The rider is training the horse to jump over obstacles.
ZH: 他准备好了，现在骑上了一匹白马。
EN: He is ready and now rides a white horse.
ZH: 自由的马在草地上奔跑。
EN: The free horse runs on the grass.
ZH: 这匹马是在赛场上获胜的。
EN: This horse is the winner on the race track.
ZH: 黑骏马是国王的最爱。
EN: The black stallion is the king's favorite.
ZH: 骑手在山上骑着匹马。
EN: The rider is riding a horse in the mountains.
ZH: 他向我展示了他训练的匹马。
EN: He showed me the horse he had trained.
ZH: 村里的每个人都有他们自己的匹马。
EN: Everyone in the village has their own horse.
